<p>John and Dave are back after their Thanksgiving break and have put together a fantastic show for you. Well, YOU have put together a fantastic show for them, because it&rsquo;s your questions about converting Word and Pages documents, printer issues, splitting and sharing USB and Ethernet, and more that are the basis for this week&rsquo;s Premium episode. Subscribe today (it&rsquo;s only $25!), support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
